ph%E1%BB%A5-h%C3%A0nh/poem-KJN5tsLol60-b4VrQaFSQw">Man phụ hành - 蠻婦行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/author-2eyz08Vw3mwjAHFJik43sA">Cao Bá Quát</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/Quy-th%E1%BB%B1/poem-4ZKH9M33U7wWwibYrQhplQ">Quy thự - 歸墅</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/author-9iJ5oLtFQBkuT0Ej5xvn9Q">Lý Thương Ẩn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/C%E1%BB%A9u-Ch%E1%BB%89-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/T%C3%A2m-ph%C3%A1p/poem-Dc1RAu1eTyEzkSUeioAEoA">Tâm pháp - 心法</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/C%E1%BB%A9u-Ch%E1%BB%89-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/author-XUD5ixNK3SYGyaOqvdYtYw">Cứu Chỉ thiền sư</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Vi-%E1%BB%A8ng-V%E1%BA%ADt/T%E1%BB%91ng-Ph%E1%BA%A7n-Th%C3%A0nh-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-ch%E1%BB%A7-b%E1%BA%A1/poem-GIwcapjLQsJZ_BVQX5su5A">Tống Phần Thành Vương chủ bạ - 送汾城王主簿</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Vi-%E1%BB%A8ng-V%E1%BA%ADt/author-XjaOXRT7NSnPjyRhhrtiSQ">Vi Ứng Vật</a>)<br></div>	</div>
